Keywords: Amiga Guide to ALL big Scene Parties
Requires: about 1Mb ChipMem
Version:  2/97  (2 of 3 in 1997, rel. 05-Jun-97)


THE SCENE GUIDE - LIFE IS A PARTY!


WHAT IS IT?

  "The Scene Guide" (current issue is 2 of 3 in 1997)
  is a fat AMIGA GUIDE ABOUT *ALL BIG* AMIGA PARTIES,
  presenting the  results of the competitions of each
  party and new party invitations, with very detailed
  information about each production.

NUMBERS OF THIS ISSUE:

  - more than 1100 Kb of plain ascii-text !
  - 2 pictures
  - 2 modules
  - 264 parties !
  - 1936 productions !

WHAT`S NEW?

  What`s new in this issue? - Added 225 productions
  and 42 parties;  many reviews  and opinions added
  and much other cool things!

